summary: This is an internal FBI Director's morning news briefing document from February 22, 2019, distributed to FBI employees. It contains news summaries with hyperlinks to full newspaper articles, and its content is restricted by copyright and contractual obligations.
keyFacts: The document is an internal FBI Director's AM News Briefing dated February 22, 2019.
It is marked as copyrighted material for internal FBI employee use only and cannot be redistributed without express written consent from Bulletin Intelligence.
The briefing contains hypertext links to full-text newspaper articles and an interactive table of contents.
The document is part of the Epstein case files under identifier EFTA00160964.
